ieser Klientel.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Dez 2019) 0aMedicinexClinical MedicinexClinical Medicine, other. 0aMedicinexClinical MedicinexPsychiatry, Psychotherapy. 4aAlkohol. 4aBehinderung. 4aFASD Erwachsene. 4aFASD-Diagnostik. 4aFASD-Screening. 4aFASD. 4aSucht. 70(DE-601)1047978780(DE-588)4217161-1aSuchtgefährdung2gnd 70(DE-601)1056504390(DE-588)4137391-1aFetale Alkoholspektrumstörung2gnd 70(DE-601)1063367540(DE-588)4015431-2aErwachsener2gnd 7aMEDICAL / Drug Guides.2bisacsh1 aBecker, Gela, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.1 aHennicke, Klaus, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.1 aKlein, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt.1 aLandgraf, Mirjam.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2015z9783110438758oZDB-23-DPM0 cEPUBz97831104195590 cprintz978311042511640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110419269423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110419269.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA1ALL  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DPMb2015